{"tid":1012821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"遺體身份確認　卡迪夫城沙拿證實遇難　","createTime":"2019-02-08T01:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T14:30:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":113,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ea71fccfe5fc04bc310a2c60c846101e1952b2","tid":1012821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dy1lKL9UwAASXHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDy1lKL9UwAASXHz.jpg&h=994b78d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國多塞特郡警方表示，從失事小型飛機殘骸中尋獲的遺體已經證實為卡迪夫城前鋒伊美利安奴沙拿。<br />\n<br />\n由南特轉投卡迪夫城的28歲阿根廷前鋒伊美利安奴沙拿，1月21日晚上乘坐由機師伊保臣駕駛的小型飛機前往卡城途中在英吉利海峽附近失去聯絡，飛機殘骸於周日上午被發現，在殘骸中發現的一具遺體則於周三成功打撈，多塞特郡警方周四證實遺體正是沙拿。<br />\n<br />\n警方在聲明中表示︰「今日2019年2月7日星期四被帶到波特蘭島的遺體，已正式確認是職業足球員伊美利安奴沙拿。」至於機師伊保臣目前仍然下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n卡城沙拿於1月21日晚上失去聯絡後，英國根西島警方搜救三日後終止行動，不過沙拿經理人發起網上眾籌，籌得324,000鎊，搜救行動得以繼續。私人搜救團隊與英國航空事故調查局（AAIB）合作，其後發現飛機殘骸及一具遺體，惟由於天氣惡劣，發機殘骸未能成功打撈，有關行動暫時已結束。"},{"pid":"2953c74b310775989e2e61d2e239d94233b7712d","tid":1012821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:19:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190208/59234392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F59234392&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=0ba06ad7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F59234392&h=346f6b0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190208/59234392</a>"},{"pid":"dd3403ad9cec4b9c988f17eb9521a8d48ebc8fff","tid":1012821,"uid":21488,"like":8,"dislike":62,"score":-54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs:南特fans~"},{"pid":"ea38140642616c8307821c